sys-kernel/genkernel

Ebuild originally added Dec. 12, 2006
Added by Fabio Erculiani <lxnay@sabayonlinux.org>

The purpose of this ebuild is to have better unionFS support
as well as auFS support in the initramfs, it is mainly used
by our liveCD.

======
16.06.08 - Wael Nasreddine <wael.nasreddine@sabayonlinux.org>
           - Version bump to 3.4.10
           - Add unionFS support back, it has been removed in gentoo's mainline.
           - Merge my own patch, verbose before asking for LUKS password.
